{"type": "article", "id": 23524, "title": "Stefan Borseliu 推出的沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-09T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110333T7NZhrBtMm1Uc0bf.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组沙发来自瑞典设计师 Stefan Borseliu 和瑞典家具品牌Fogia，扶手是椭圆形的，靠垫和坐垫都近似于厚实的枕头，给人柔和舒适的感受。支撑沙发的结构是细的橡木腿，以衬托出沙发的宽阔。设计师称形状的灵感源于梵蒂冈的坎波广场 （Piazza del Campo)，大概是因为广场带给人的典雅和温暖。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110331Hr8w3B7hc4mJf2LP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.77350427\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110332TWjvsn0YBU7IiMft.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021103327mLuwWa4bVXxFpz9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54487179\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110333KxqyUanGQjSLVzA7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}